CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 7, 1950, pg. 7 reads: "Grace Cornerstone Laying - At impressive ceremonies conducted by Pittsburgh masons, the cornerstone of the Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church at Bryn Mawr Road and Iowa Street was laid on Sunday, Sept. 24. The Rev. Harold R. Tolliver is pastor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man, two ministers, including Rev. Harold R. Tolliver on left, and woman, walking outside of Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church for cornerstone laying ceremony
